{"tid":1947641,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(冷知識) 風靡全球的JTV同Twitch.tv係由華人創立","createTime":"2020-03-28T12:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:58:31.000Z","uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0239a387b830b858cff97d238641be4553d8189","tid":1947641,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/17/Jtv-Logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F17%2FJtv-Logo.png&h=1e998289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJTV，原名Justin.tv，是一個在2007年3月由耶魯大學學生簡側田（Justin Kan）創立的網站，概念與YouTube相若，讓網民於網上分享影片。 總部位于美國加利福尼亞州舊金山。它是一個可即時聊天的個人線上音樂與影音串流平台。<br />\n<br />\n2011年6月，分割出聚焦於電子遊戲直播的網站「Twitch」。Twitch是遊戲軟體影音串流平台，從Justin.tv分割成立於2011年6月6日。提供平台供遊戲玩家進行遊戲過程的實況，或供遊戲賽事的轉播。也提供聊天室，讓觀眾間進行簡單的互動。除了遊戲內容的串流，也允許實況進行Creative、Music、Social Eating等非遊戲的內容。<br />\n<br />\n2014年2月，Twitch.tv與Justin.Tv的母公司改名為「Twitch Interactive」[1]。同年8月5日，Justin.tv終止服務<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0224/20190224102038565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0224%2F20190224102038565.jpg&h=c2aae5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJustin Kan（1983年&mdash;）係美籍華裔嘅互聯網創業家、網絡視頻平臺 Justin.tv 同 Twitch嘅聯合創始人，亦係移動影視分享平臺Socialcam嘅創始人。Justin Kan喺2005年從耶魯大學畢業，先後賣咗自己創立嘅Kiko、Socialcam、Exec等嘅網站；2014年，將自己同Emmett <a href=\"http://Shear聯合創辦嘅Twitch賣畀Amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FShear%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E5%98%85Twitch%E8%B3%A3%E7%95%80Amazon.com&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=8749afcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Shear聯合創辦嘅Twitch賣畀Amazon.com</a>，賣得9億7000萬美元，而家係矽谷培育新創企業Y Combinator機構嘅拍檔。 <br />\n<br />\n大家快D入黎叨光<br />\n我是中國人呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624fa215443439fe86be1b8600fdacbfe5ae79ed","tid":1947641,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"個姓已經唔係用拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2929cc47183c5ca246785f11f006a6f6917f7571","tid":1947641,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"頂以為係咸網"},{"pid":"1fb86e6468660bb153f48ee9c7084e5f40a80020","tid":1947641,"uid":42665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2929cc47183c5ca246785f11f006a6f6917f7571","tid":1947641,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"頂以為係咸網"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:11:08.000Z","msg":"jtv都唔識<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw懷念以前好多好正嘅直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n索尼講波"},{"pid":"71414c779905ed2412c80314ba548ae6a69dc279","tid":1947641,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9663c27f6b4997f4275bc70a3167d80dac66ac","tid":1947641,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d18c0554ef83eb3426b6c74b776445b87fb80f5","tid":1947641,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"冇達哥用有撚人識佢咩"},{"pid":"1c94b963ccc9c2218726f2283a92994f4bff9d37","tid":1947641,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"賣得9億7000萬美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.